Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.60,mid_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}鏡の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.17,mid_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}はい　はいー
